snippet.title: Johnny Depp Gets BIG WIN Over Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Gets BIG WIN Over Amber Heard
Subscribe Here 👉 http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3f6toBU

If you recall earlier this year Johnny Depp had lost his case and the appeal for his high court libel ruling. The judge sided with The Sun newspaper who deemed their article on Depp to be substantially true. Now months removed from that loss, Johnny Depp has finally scored a massive win against Amber Heard.
